<p>These numbers include typical add-ons like inventory management, marketing tools, and integrations. Both platforms require 12-month contracts, with ServiceTitan often pushing 24-36 month agreements for better pricing.</p>

<p>The real kicker? Implementation costs. FieldEdge charges $3,000-8,000 for setup depending on data migration complexity. ServiceTitan's implementation ranges from $8,000-25,000, including mandatory training sessions that can add weeks to your go-live timeline.</p>

